latestPosts.caption:
Cheesy, crunchy, and packed with protein? Say less. 😮‍💨 This grain bowl topped with homemade queso and crushed-up Cowboy Cheddar Cheezmos is about to be your new go-to lunch. It’s bold, balanced, and ridiculously satisfying! 🧀✨

🥗 Grain Bowl
Base of arugula (~1 cup) 
Brown rice 
Black beans 
Roasted sweet potatoes 
Roasted broccoli 

🧀 Homemade Cheezmos High Protein Queso
1 1/2 cup cottage cheese 
1/3 cup nutritional yeast 
1-2 tbsp cumin (per preference – we love 2 tbsp) 
1 tbsp garlic powder 
1 tbsp chili powder 
** Blend everything together – mix in some crushed up Cheezmos for extra crunch and pour over this high protein queso over the top of the grain bowl for a cheesy & protein packed sauce!

Recipe by @sophs.clean.eats 💛
